v(s) &amp;amp;= \max_{a \in \mathcal{A}(s)} \left[ \sum_{r} p(r|s, a)r + \gamma \sum_{s&amp;#x27;} p(s&amp;#x27;|s, a)v(s&amp;#x27;) \right] \\
&amp;amp;= \max_{\pi} \sum_{a \in \mathcal{A}(s)} \pi(a|s) \left[ \sum_{r} p(r|s, a)r + \gamma \sum_{s&amp;#x27;} p(s&amp;#x27;|s, a)v(s&amp;#x27;) \right]
\end{align*}
