\Pr_{\pi}(s|s&amp;#x27;) = \sum_{k=0}^{\infty} \gamma^{k} [P_{\pi}^{k}]_{s&amp;#x27;s} = [(I - \gamma P_{\pi})^{-1}]_{s&amp;#x27;s}
